{"title":"如此“走向世界”","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":3,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"如此“走向世界”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫画韦启美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"配诗池北偶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一味崇洋媚外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今大有人在。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论精华糟粕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统统顶礼膜拜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"标榜“走向世界”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打出“接轨”招牌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"言必希腊罗马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记祖宗三代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要民族风格，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要民族气派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昧着艺术良心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖弄小技歪才。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎合洋人口味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博取廉价喝彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此等名流大家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可鄙而又可哀。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":11,"page_end":11}